{"tid":1745642,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實政府會唔會好驚佔左理大？","createTime":"2019-11-22T10:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T11:31:09.000Z","uid":20416,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"436c312d061bef4ed2586ef5d58441970a691b26","tid":1745642,"uid":20416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:22:33.000Z","msg":"點解一定扮攻入去，迫你地走出黎<br />\n如果淨係想拎返啲道路，趕完啲人入去咪得<br />\n<br />\n會唔會其實怕慢慢更多人去佔領 好似雨傘咁<br />\n當太多人係入面果時 根本唔可以咁樣攻入去<br />\n所以速戰快速決<br />\n<br />\n諗諗下 其實佔領左理大 唔同金鐘<br />\n理大有條主要幹道<br />\n大把空間休息 作支援<br />\n煮野食 急救 什至 武器等等<br />\n地形難攻 <br />\n無可能再好似雨傘咁抬你走<br />\n<br />\n當慢慢佔領風氣大左 佔埋中大 吐露港<br />\n浸大加城大 獅子山 基本成個香港唔洗運作<br />\n而警力迫住分散 <br />\n<br />\n參考返烏克蘭 都係佔左廣場做base<br />\n但佔領一定要有軍事知識<br />\n如何做安檢 訂立規則 分工 設立防線等等"},{"pid":"9d22e780f4e0786a62370413ce851843e86a5b77","tid":1745642,"uid":257111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:24:29.000Z","msg":"咁不如我地佔領外圍 包圍返啲曱甴"},{"pid":"bf6fce568800ee96ebd28ff08d1daf4c4d3c33a0","tid":1745642,"uid":20416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d22e780f4e0786a62370413ce851843e86a5b77","tid":1745642,"uid":257111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:24:29.000Z","msg":"咁不如我地佔領外圍 包圍返啲曱甴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:25:48.000Z","msg":"咁點算佔領"},{"pid":"ba717c9f47460a2f80f79abb44bddeb6912418e2","tid":1745642,"uid":297672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:25:59.000Z","msg":"人類總係要_____.jpg"},{"pid":"41559e6680b6b4309ebf58c04798e36b6f894a79","tid":1745642,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:26:55.000Z","msg":"poly某同學 ：祝全部俾人拉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Sdhr7X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Sdhr7X.png&h=b4b8b6d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c415ebacd3665e3c473b6b4e227032616447b54","tid":1745642,"uid":56633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T